    "terms-mechanisms": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 4 terms/mechanisms \u2014 **chunk_id** per contract; **mechanisms** use **realized_by** \u2192 story map paths; procedural **steps[]** on stories, not duplicated in mechanisms. No promoted concepts[] yet.",
    "shaped-story-map": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 5 **shaped_story_map.json** \u2014 **evidence_chunk_ids[]**; optional **steps[]** / **realizes_mechanism** for mechanism linkage; rule **shaped-story-shape** (+ **scanners.json**). Read **shaped-story-map.md**.",
    "domain-types": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 6 sparse types \u2014 promotion bar, **owns**, evidence; story map precedes types (rule **story-map-before-domain-types**).",
    "variant-classification": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 7 variant representation \u2014 explicit per-family decisions **before** deep property work (rule **variant-decisions-before-deepen**).",
    "deepen": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 8 deepen \u2014 responsibilities, depends_on, no anemic/god concepts; approved tooling only (rule **deepen-approved-tools-only**).",
    "integrate": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 9 integrate \u2014 one coherent map/model/spec; drain candidate queue; cross-cutting resolved or deferred in writing.",
    "validate": "**Focus (this phase):** Phase 10 gates \u2014 **build.py** pipeline, **evidence-citations-required** scanner, **class-diagram** (layout checks on `map-model-class-diagram.drawio`), manifest, reproducible reports."
